	*** lupe - real-time magnifying glass for X11 ***

----------------------------------------------------------------
* About

Lupe is a magnifying glass for X Window System.
Lupe likes xmag. But, update image real-time,
and needs more processor power.

----------------------------------------------------------------
* Install

% xmkmf
% make
and executable binary "lupe" is created.
Move this file to install directory as you like.
% mv lupe /usr/local/bin

Copy manual source file "lupe.man" to manual install directory.
% cp lupe.man /usr/local/man/man1/lupe.1x

----------------------------------------------------------------
* Use

% lupe
to start lupe, and display magnified image of
the area pointed by mouse pointer.

To know options. type lupe usage
% lupe -help
or read manual page. (or read sources)

